Lot 3 (Port.) of Proc. 423 (Lower Bicutan)

A PARCEL OF LAND (Lot 3 (Port.) of Proc. 423), situated in Barangay Lower Bicutan, Municipality of Taguig, Province of Metro Manila, Island of Luzon. Bounded on the W., N., E., SW., & NW., along lines 1-2-3-4-5 Lot 4 (Port. Proc . 423).

Beginning at a point marked “1” of Lot 3, being S. 26-53′ W., 5045.49 m. from BLLM No. 1, Cadm-590-D, Taguig, Cad. Mapping, thence:

